name: WestJet's INAUGURAL Calgary to Dublin Flight! 787-9 Business Class
description:
On June 1st, 2019, WestJet inaugurated flights between Calgary and Dublin, with their new Boeing 787-9 Dreamliner.

Unlike the other two inaugurals, which I only filmed from outside, I was on board!

Thanks to some very generous people at WestJet, I also got to experience what their Business Class is like on a transatlantic flight! See what I thought of the whole experience in this very special trip report.

Special thank you to Sean for the departure photos: https://www.facebook.com/SCCurriePhotography/
